study ID	author	iadl ax	variable	ppt	n	stat	effect size
66	McDougall et al., (2010)	DAFS-R	mmse	nc	45	pcc	0.57
60	Lima-Silva et al., (2015)	DAFS-R	mmse	nc	34	src	0.24
